What you need to know:

Kipchoge became the first man to ever run a full marathon, 42.195km, under two hours when he clocked 1:59:40 in Vienna, Austria in 2019In a statement, his management said that they had decided to document his journey as an inspiration to humanity in a movie titled, ‘The Last Milestone!’The inspirational documentary, which was executively produced by Academy Award nominee Ridley Scott and directed by Jake Scott, will receive its digital release on August 23